line_1: As Mem'ry paints his former feats,
line_2: With sudden stamp the ground he beats,

line_1: Her starting damsels sprung from mossy feats,
line_2: Dropp'd from their gauzy laps the gather'd sweets,

line_1: Old play-bills, ASTLEY'S last year's feats,

line_2: Robb'ry of gardens, quarrels in the streets,
She shrinks, and hides her in the plaits:

line_1: And yet, for all my fending feats,
line_2: Molly was forc'd to change the sheets;
